These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, mystery, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, trike, bus
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the trike##2
6. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | martial-arts     | mystery | family |
| Transport     | airplane     | trike | bus  | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, punk, soul, d&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, boat, roller, train
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | punk    | d&b     | soul  |
| Transport     | taxi    | roller | boat | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, punk, classical, funk
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, chinchilla, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
2. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | classical   | country  | funk |
| Pet           | hamster | hedgehog | chinchilla | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, reading, gardening, skydiving
There are 4 different nationalities: british, japanese, thai, malaysian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the thai##2
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
4. the thai is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the british is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | reading | video-games | skydiving | gardening  |
| Nationality   | japanese  | british   | malaysian  | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, tea, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, traveling, magic-tricks, baking
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | sprite   | tea | iced-tea    |
| Hobby      | traveling | sudoku | magic-tricks       | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, iced-tea, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, ship, helicopter
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the ship and the person drinking milk##2
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | milk | iced-tea | water | mirinda |
| Transport   | bike | quad-bike  | ship    | helicopter  |

