.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, argentine, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, boat, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the argentine is between the australian and the american##2
5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the boat and the american##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | american | argentine | australian     |
| Transport     | skateboard | jet-ski  | quad-bike   | boat |

