.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, reading, puzzles, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, action, satire, thriller
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching action movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | hiking | puzzles | writing | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | action | satire | spy      | thriller |

