.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, hedgehog, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding, weightlifting, surfing
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the rat is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | ferret | rat   | hedgehog      | cat      |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | weightlifting | cycling | surfing |

