.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, gospel, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, spanish, australian, brazilian
1. the malaysian is on the right of the spanish##1
2. the fan of gospel is between the brazilian and the spanish##2
3. the fan of hip-hop is the spanish##1
4. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the malaysian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | hip-hop | gospel      | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | australian  | spanish    | malaysian | brazilian |

