.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, cooking, rock-climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bus, ship, quad-bike
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | fishing | cooking | rock-climbing    | collecting      |
| Transport   | ship       | quad-bike       | bus | van |

