3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
