.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, polish, british, chinese
4 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, lizard, chinchilla
1. the polish is on the far right##1
2. the italian is the italian##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the polish##3
5. the british is on the left or right of the chinese##3
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the chinese##3
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | italian | british  | chinese | polish |
| Pet           | lizard     | chinchilla | goat    | mouse     |

