.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, banana, orange, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, paramedic, chef, freelancer
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
2. the paramedic is on the right of the chef##1
3. the person eating banana is on the left of the social-worker##1
4. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | banana  | raspberry | watermelon  | orange      |
| Job    | freelancer | social-worker | chef | paramedic |

