1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of soul is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
