.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo, surfing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water     | sprite     | iced-tea          | juice |
| Sport      | swimming | water-polo | lacrosse | surfing  |

 